name: bitCount
desc: Returns the number of one-bits in the two's complement binary representation of the specified long value.

name: byteValue
desc: Returns the value of this Long as a byte.

name: compare
desc: Compares two long values numerically.

name: compareTo
desc: Compares two Long objects numerically.

name: decode
desc: Decodes a String into a Long.

name: doubleValue
desc: Returns the value of this Long as a double.

name: equals
desc: Compares this object to the specified object.

name: floatValue
desc: Returns the value of this Long as a float.

name: getLong
desc: Determines the long value of the system property with the specified name.

name: getLong
desc: Determines the long value of the system property with the specified name.

name: getLong
desc: Returns the long value of the system property with the specified name.

name: hashCode
desc: Returns a hash code for this Long.

name: highestOneBit
desc: Returns a long value with at most a single one-bitt, in the position of the highest-order ("leftmost") one-bit in the specified long value.

name: intValue
desc: Returns the value of this Long as an int.

name: longValue
desc: Returns the value of this Long as a long value.

name: lowestOneBit
desc: Returns a long value with at most a single one-bit, in the position of the lowest-order ("rightmost") one-bit in the specified long value.

name: numberOfLeadingZeros
desc: Returns the number of zero bits preceding the highest-order ("leftmost") one-bit in the two's complement binary representation of the specified long value.

name: numberOfTrailingZeros
desc: Returns the number of zero bits following the lowest-order ("rightmost") one-bit in the two's complement binary representation of the specified long value.

name: parseLong
desc: Parses the string argument as a signed decimal long.

name: parseLong
desc: Parses the string argument as a signed long in the radix specified by the second argument.

name: reverse
desc: Returns the value obtained by reversing the order of the bits in the two's complement binary representation of the specified long value.

name: reverseBytes
desc: Returns the value obtained by reversing the order of the bytes in the two's complement representation of the specified long value.

name: rotateLeft
desc: Returns the value obtained by rotating the two's complement binary representation of the specified long value left by the specified number of bits.

name: rotateRight
desc: Returns the value obtained by rotating the two's complement binary representation of the specified long value right by the specified number of bits.

name: shortValue
desc: Returns the value of this Long as a short.

name: signum
desc: Returns the signum function of the specified long value.

name: toBinaryString
desc: Returns a string representation of the long argument as an unsigned integer in base 2.

name: toHexString
desc: Returns a string representation of the long argument as an unsigned integer in base 16.

name: toOctalString
desc: Returns a string representation of the long argument as an unsigned integer in base 8.

name: toString
desc: Returns a String object representing this Long's value.

name: toString
desc: Returns a String object representing the specified long.

name: toString
desc: Returns a string representation of the first argument in the radix specified by the second argument.

name: valueOf
desc: Returns a Long instance representing the specified long value.

name: valueOf
desc: Returns a Long object holding the value of the specified String.

name: valueOf
desc: Returns a Long object holding the value extracted from the specified String when parsed with the radix given by the second argument.
